name: Sakura Village
description: Welcome to "Sakura Village", a limited edition NFT collection inspired by the gaming adventures of Sakura Tanaka, known for her mastery of the gaming world. Dive into the digital realm and own a piece of Sakura's virtual legacy with these exclusive NFTs.

name: Sakura's Hong Kong Chronicles
description: Embark on a virtual journey through the bustling streets of Hong Kong with "Sakura's Hong Kong Chronicles," an exclusive NFT collection inspired by Tanaka Sakura's gaming escapades in vibrant urban landscapes.
